'''俄罗斯－赞比亚关系'''（{{lang-ru|Российско-замбийские отношения}}），是指[[俄羅斯聯邦|俄羅斯聯邦]]和[[尚比亞共和國|尚比亞共和國]]之間的雙邊關係。俄羅斯於贊比亞首都[[盧薩卡|盧薩卡]]設有大使館，贊比亞亦在[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]設大使館。

== 歷史 ==
在贊比亞於1964年10月24日從[[英國|英國]]獨立後<ref>{{cite news|url=http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F60813F63E581B728DDDAD0A94D8415B848AF1D3|title=Northern Rhodesia Reborn as Zambia; Britain Ends Rule|last=Conley|first=Robert|date=24 October 1964|publisher=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|page=1|accessdate=2009-07-26|archive-date=2012-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103184403/http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F60813F63E581B728DDDAD0A94D8415B848AF1D3|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]發送電報，承認贊比亞獨立，並表示願意與其建交<ref name="sovtreaties">{{cite book|last=Ginsburgs|first=George|coauthors=Slusser, Robert M.|title=A calendar of Soviet treaties, 1958-1973|publisher=[[Brill_Publishers|BRILL]]|year=1981|isbn=90-286-0609-2|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=3X4nnE7eKjEC|page=908|accessdate=2009-07-27|archive-date=2013-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130623040742/http://books.google.com/books?id=3X4nnE7eKjEC|dead-url=no}}</ref>；兩國隨後於1964年10月30日正式建立外交關係<ref name="sovtreaties" />。兩國關係於1976年曾一度惡化<ref name="donaldson">{{cite book|last=Donaldson|first=Robert H.|coauthors=Papp, Daniel S.|title=The Soviet Union in the Third World|publisher=[[Taylor_&_Francis|Taylor & Francis]]|year=1981|page=89|chapter=The Soviet Union and Southern Africa|isbn=0-89158-974-0|url=http://books.google.com.au/books?id=xPcNAAAAQAAJ|accessdate=2009-07-27|archive-date=2011-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110610223529/http://books.google.com.au/books?id=xPcNAAAAQAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.time.com/time/printout/0,8816,917969,00.html|title=ANGOLA: A Tiger at the Back Door|date=9 February 1976|publisher=[[Time_Magazine|Time Magazine]]|accessdate=2009-07-26|archive-date=2013-02-04|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130204133834/http://www.time.com/time/printout/0,8816,917969,00.html}}</ref>，但其後有改善，蘇聯更在1979年到1983年向贊比亞出口軍火<ref name="heritage">{{cite web |url=http://s3.amazonaws.com/thf_media/1986/pdf/bg525.pdf |title=Moscow's Strategy in Southern Africa: A Country by Country Review |last=Pascoe |first=William |date=21 July 1986 |publisher=[[Heritage_Foundation|Heritage Foundation]] |accessdate=2010-08-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5ryW1YWHY?url=http://s3.amazonaws.com/thf_media/1986/pdf/bg525.pdf |archivedate=2010-08-14 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[蘇聯解體|蘇聯解體]]後，贊比亞於1991年12月31日宣佈承認俄羅斯聯邦<ref name="polpredzamrus">{{ru icon}} {{cite web|url=http://www.polpred.com/?cnt=55&art=2588|title=Замбия. Связи с Россией и СНГ|publisher=Polpred.com|accessdate=2009-07-26|archive-date=2011-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110105181910/http://polpred.com/?cnt=55&art=2588|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 經濟關係 ==
俄羅斯和贊比亞簽署了雙邊協議，保障貿易和經濟關係；蘇聯和贊比亞亦曾於1971年12月17日簽訂貿易協議<ref name="polpredzamrus" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://docs.google.com/untreaty.un.org/unts/1_60000/26/27/00051306.pdf|title=Trade Agreement between the Government of the Union of Soviet Socialist Republics and the Government of the Republic of Zambia|last=[[Government_of_the_Soviet_Union|Government of the Soviet Union]]|coauthors=[[Government_of_Zambia|Government of Zambia]]|date=17 December 1971|location=[[Lusaka|Lusaka]]|publisher=[[United_Nations_Treaty_Series|United Nations Treaty Series]]|accessdate=2009-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121106181841/http://docs.google.com/untreaty.un.org/unts/1_60000/26/27/00051306.pdf|archive-date=2012-11-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2007年，兩國的雙邊貿易總額為1140萬美元；2008年，兩國的雙邊貿易總額增加至1,700萬美元。贊比亞到俄羅斯的出口產品主要為[[煙草|煙草]]，而俄羅斯出口到贊比亞的產品包括[[農業機械|農業機械]]、[[摩托車|摩托車]]和[[食物|食物]]<ref name="zambiamid">{{ru icon}} {{cite web|url=http://www.mid.ru/ns-rafr.nsf/89414576079db559432569d8002421fc/432569a40037340743256c3a0047948d?OpenDocument|title=Российско-замбийские отношения|date=17 February 2009|publisher=[[Russian_Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs|Russian Ministry of Foreign Affairs]]|accessdate=2009-07-26|archive-date=2012-05-01|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67KSbvQ9J?url=http://www.mid.ru/ns-rafr.nsf/89414576079db559432569d8002421fc/432569a40037340743256c3a0047948d?OpenDocument|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 文化關係 ==
1966年8月25日，蘇聯和贊比亞政府簽署了文化合作的協議，協議至今日的俄羅斯聯邦時代仍然生效<ref name="agreements">{{ru icon}} {{cite web|url=http://www.mid.ru/ns-rafr.nsf/89414576079db559432569d8002421fc/f7b431475dc324ffc3257121003d85f9?OpenDocument|title=Двусторонние документы|date=1 March 2006|publisher=[[Russian_Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs|Russian Ministry of Foreign Affairs]]|accessdate=2009-07-26|archive-date=2012-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120914181808/http://www.mid.ru/ns-rafr.nsf/89414576079db559432569d8002421fc/f7b431475dc324ffc3257121003d85f9?OpenDocument|dead-url=no}}</ref>。於1989年，於盧薩卡開設了俄羅斯文化科學中心。此中心與盧薩卡駐俄羅斯大使館合作，舉行目的為加強俄羅斯和贊比亞兩國關係的活動，並向公眾提供關於俄羅斯內外政策的信息，又提供[[俄語|俄語]]培訓<ref>{{ru icon}} {{cite web|url=http://www.rs-gov.ru/node/1522|title=Замбия|publisher=[[Federal_Agency_for_Commonwealth_of_Independent_States,_Compatriots_Living_Abroad_and_International_Humanitarian_Cooperation|Federal Agency for Commonwealth of Independent States, Compatriots Living Abroad and International Humanitarian Cooperation]]|accessdate=2009-07-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090831081338/http://www.rs-gov.ru/node/1522|archivedate=2009-08-31}}</ref>。截至2009年，約450名贊比亞學生在俄羅斯留學，俄羅斯政府亦有向他們提供獎學金<ref name="zambiamid" />。

